    def __init__(self, value):
        self.value = value

    # 请在此处填空
    def __add__(self, other):
        return CustomNumber(self.value + other.value)

# 使用示例
result = CustomNumber(5) + CustomNumber(3)
```

[答案] `def __add__(self, other):`

